---
title: Green Machine Pumpkin Ravioli with Tomato Sugo & Apple Salad
description: These ravioli are packed with big flavours thanks to the earthy sweetness from the pumpkin. To balance out all that
personality, we’re adding a tomato-based sauce for its abundant flavour contribution. The result is a colourful,
hearty dish that’s guaranteed to become a pasta-night classic in your home.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
